<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA52">
<l>māṇpāvit taññāṉṟu maṇṇirantāṉ māyavaḷnañ</l>
<l>cūṇpāvit tuṇṭāṉa tōruruvaṅ kāṇpāṉnaṅ</l>
<l>kaṇṇavā maṟṟoṉṟu kāṇuṟā cīrparavā</l>
<l>tuṇṇavāy tāṉuṟumō voṉṟu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To see the singular form of him who that day begged for the earth,</l>
<l>having contemplated honour, who ate, having contemplated it as food,</l>
<l>the poison of the deceitful one,</l>
<l>without our eye having desire to see any other thing, will [our] mouth</l>
<l>have anything to eat without revering [his] excellence?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
